sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    participant User as Developer
    participant Ingest as Ingest Layer (API)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (State)
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ (Queue)
    participant Forge as Forge Engine (Worker)
    participant Pulse as Pulse Cluster (K8s)
    participant Kaniko as Build Tool (Kaniko)
    participant Registry as Registry

    Note over User,Registry: === STAGE 1: INGEST ===
    
    User->>Ingest: POST /api/apps/{id}/deploy
    Ingest->>DB: Create Build (QUEUED)
    Ingest->>MQ: Publish BuildRequestedEvent
    Ingest-->>User: 202 Accepted {buildId}
    
    Note over User,Registry: === STAGE 2: FORGE ===
    
    MQ->>Forge: Consume event
    Forge->>DB: Update Build (BUILDING)
    Forge->>Pulse: Create Build Pod (Kaniko)
    
    loop Stream Logs
        Kaniko->>Forge: Pod logs
        Forge-->>User: WebSocket (Live Logs)
    end
    
    Kaniko->>Registry: Push image
    Forge->>DB: Update Build (SUCCESS)
    
    Note over User,Registry: === STAGE 3: PULSE ===
    
    Forge->>Pulse: Apply Deployment/Service/Ingress
    Forge->>DB: Create Deployment (HEALTHY)
    Pulse-->>User: 🚀 Live at: app.project.kubelite.local
